{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781957327703,"sessionID":"ses_11b117861ffeRAkl3UtZo4HlZk","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"397829899","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Cache API\n\nA simple in-memory cache implementation that provides methods for storing and retrieving key-value pairs.\n\n## Usage\n\n```js\nimport { createCache } from './cache.mjs'\n\nconst cache = createCache()\n```\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates a new cache instance that manages key-value storage internally. Returns an object with cache methods `get`, `set`, `delete`, and `clear`.\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves a value by key from the cache. Returns the cached value if it exists, otherwise returns `undefined`.\n\n```js\nconst value = cache.get(key)\n```\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nStores a value in the cache with the given key. Returns the stored value.\n\n```js\ncache.set('my-key', 'my-value')\nconst saved = cache.set('my-key', 'my-value') // Returns: 'my-value'\n```\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves an entry from the cache by key. Returns the previous value if the key existed, otherwise returns `undefined`.\n\n```js\ncache.delete(key)\n```\n\n### clear()\n\nRemoves all entries from the cache.\n\n```js\ncache.clear()\n```\n","filePath":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-20T06-38-17-288Z/openslimedit-docs-from-code-2/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-20T06-38-17-288Z/openslimedit-docs-from-code-2/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","time":{"start":1781957327691,"end":1781957327700}},"id":"prt_ee4eee007001XctCArdgq5isfK","sessionID":"ses_11b117861ffeRAkl3UtZo4HlZk","messageID":"msg_ee4eedca800179DoDi0A1187l7"}}
